{"tid":1467543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼你老母","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:43.000Z","uid":263311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e3443bc3843941e94ebf13e76c1ceeaeb3ad14","tid":1467543,"uid":263311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"鬼一向都有，絕對唔係呢幾日先有<br />\n捉鬼係唔會令到場運動贏<br />\n只會令到大家愈來愈分化！<br />\n<br />\n我相信前線手足係有勇有謀既！<br />\n我地要切記保持冷靜理智<br />\n如遇到有人<span style=\"color: red;\">情緒過於激動、試圖帶頭做大家唔認同既野</span><br />\n夾走佢，勸佢返屋企抖下就OK！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔駛刻意捉鬼<br />\n杜絕一切互屌！</span><br />\n<br />\n不篤灰、不分化、不割蓆<br />\n堅守三大原則，我地先有勝算！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛大家！</span>"},{"pid":"d849941ce401b6966668a19ce87d787f3af02fb4","tid":1467543,"uid":263311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4413d5041e5ae8af5fc83711d75abd83735c8613","tid":1467543,"uid":263311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"11a5b6f2128e9220e274235986eb9d285f29851a","tid":1467543,"uid":263311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:43.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}